[32m│[0m ### Thoughts                                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why this payload worked:**                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. The `input` HTML tag is not filtered                                                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. The `autofocus` attribute causes automatic focus without user interaction                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. The `onfocus` event handler is not in the filter blocklist                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. When the element receives focus, `alert("XSS")` executes                                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. The challenge validates that `alert("XSS")` is triggered (not just any JavaScript)                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Filter behavior observed:**                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
