[32m│[0m - Event handlers `onerror` and `onload` are blocked, but `onfocus` is not                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The word `script` is blocked, preventing `<script>` tags                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No output encoding is applied to the `name` parameter                                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Security implications:**                                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The `x-xss-protection: 0` header explicitly disables browser XSS filtering                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Blacklist filtering is inherently bypassable                                                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The application properly validates the XSS success by detecting the alert execution                                                                [32m│[0m
