[32m│[0m ### Thoughts                                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why this payload worked:**                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. The application has a **keyword-based blocklist** rather than an allowlist approach                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. The blocklist includes: `script`, `onerror`, `onload`, `onclick`, and single quotes `'`                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. The `onfocus` event handler is **NOT in the blocklist**                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Double quotes `"` are **NOT filtered**                                                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. The `autofocus` attribute automatically triggers the `onfocus` event without user interaction                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Filter behavior observed:**                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Simple keyword matching (case-sensitive)                                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Blocks specific event handlers but not all                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Blocks single quotes but allows double quotes                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The `x-xss-protection: 0` header explicitly disables browser XSS filtering                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Security recommendation:**                                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Implement Content Security Policy (CSP)                                                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Use output encoding instead of keyword filtering                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Enable browser XSS protection (`x-xss-protection: 1; mode=block`)                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Implement allowlist validation for user input                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Never trust user input - always sanitize before rendering                                                                                          [32m│[0m
